"Whether to enable template mode. When enabled, variables in "
"``{variable_name}`` from ``message`` will be replaced from "
"``ctx['variables']``."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.ask_env:10 of
msgid "元组 ``(ctx, answer)``：更新后的上下文与环境响应。"
msgstr "Tuple ``(ctx, answer)``: Updated context and environment response."

