#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.name:1 of
msgid "智能体显示名称。"
msgstr "Agent display name."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:1 of
msgid "发送补全请求并验证响应是否符合 Pydantic 模型。"
msgstr ""
"Send a completion request and verify that the response conforms to the "
"Pydantic model."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:3 of
msgid "支持多轮对话以向 LLM 提供错误反馈并进行修正。"
msgstr ""
"Supports multiple rounds of dialogue to provide error feedback to LLM and"
" make corrections."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:5 of
msgid ""
"该方法会先向 LLM 发送请求，再从响应中提取 JSON 片段（``extract_json``）， 当整段内容本身就以 ``{`` 或 "
"``[`` 开头时回退使用全文，并统一交给 ``json_repair.loads`` 解析。随后会使用目标 Pydantic 模型进行验证； "
"如果验证失败，则立即把错误反馈给 LLM 并重试；如果遇到 429（速率限制） 错误，则改为使用二进制指数退避。最终返回验证通过的模型实例。"
msgstr ""
"This method will first send a request to LLM, and then extract the JSON "
"fragment (``extract_json``) from the response. When the entire content "
"itself begins with ``{`` or ``[``, it will fall back to the full text and"
" hand it over to ``json_repair.loads`` for parsing. The target Pydantic "
"model is then used for verification; if verification fails, the error is "
"immediately fed back to LLM and retried; if a 429 (rate limiting) error "
"is encountered, binary exponential backoff is used instead. Finally, the "
"verified model instance is returned."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:11
#: of
msgid "用于验证的 Pydantic 模型类型。"
msgstr "Pydantic model type used for validation."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:12
#: agentsociety2.agent.base.LLMInteractionHistory:8 of
msgid "发送给 LLM 的消息列表。"
msgstr "List of messages sent to LLM."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:15
#: of
msgid "最大重试次数（默认 10）。"
msgstr "Maximum number of retries (default 10)."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:16
#: of
msgid "429 错误发生时指数退避的基准延迟秒数（默认 1.0）。 仅用于 429 速率限制错误。其他错误立即重试。"
msgstr ""
"Base delay in seconds for exponential backoff when a 429 error occurs "
"(default 1.0). Only used for 429 rate limiting errors. Other errors retry"
" immediately."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:18
#: of
msgid "指数退避的最大延迟秒数（默认 60.0）。"
msgstr "Maximum delay in seconds for exponential backoff (default 60.0)."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:19
#: of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "可选的自定义错误反馈提示模板。 如为 None，将使用默认提示模板。模板应包含 ``{error_message}`` 占位符。"
msgstr ""
"Optional custom error feedback prompt template. If None, the default "
"prompt template will be used. The template should contain the "
"``{error_message}`` placeholder."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:21
#: of
msgid "传给 litellm 的单次 HTTP 超时（秒）；``None`` 表示不设置。"
msgstr "Single HTTP timeout (seconds) passed to litellm; ``None`` means not set."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:23
#: of
msgid "验证通过的 Pydantic 模型实例。"
msgstr "A verified Pydantic model instance."

#: ../../api/agent.rst ../../api/backend.rst ../../api/config.rst
#: ../../api/env.rst
#: agentsociety2.backend.routers.prefill_params.get_class_prefill_params of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr "Throw"

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:24
#: of
msgid "响应无法解析，或在所有重试后仍验证失败。"
msgstr "The response could not be parsed or validation failed after all retries."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:25
#: of
msgid "LLM 未初始化。"
msgstr "LLM is not initialized."

#: agentsociety2.agent.base.AgentBase.acompletion_with_pydantic_validation:28
#: of
msgid "二进制指数退避仅在检测到 429（速率限制）错误时应用。 对于验证错误和其他非速率限制错误，函数立即重试以向 LLM 提供更快的反馈。"
msgstr ""
"Binary exponential backoff is only applied when a 429 (rate limiting) "
"error is detected. For validation errors and other non-rate limiting "
"errors, the function retries immediately to provide faster feedback to "
"the LLM."

#: ../../api/agent.rst:18
