#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent:3 of
msgid "设计目标是让每个 Person 拥有独立线程、独立工作区和独立技能可见性， 在每个 step 内通过工具循环完成“观察-推理-行动”。"
msgstr ""
"The design goal is to allow each Person to have an independent thread, "
"independent workspace and independent skill visibility, and complete "
"\"observation-reasoning-action\" through the tool loop in each step."

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.mcp_description:1 of
