"overwrite existing files)."

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.__init__:7 of
msgid ""
"传入 ``AgentConfig.from_kwargs()`` 的扁平参数（节选）：  - "
"``max_tool_rounds``：单步最大工具轮数（默认 24） - "
"``preload_workspace_paths``：预读文件列表（注入 system prompt 的 workspace 快照） - "
"``thread_key_state_paths``：thread 压缩时附带的 KEY_STATE_JSON 文件路径列表 - "
"``system_prompt_max_identity_chars``：Agent Identity JSON 总长度上限（默认 10000） "
"- ``workspace_read_chunk_chars``：``workspace_read`` / ``read_skill`` "
"单段最大字符数（默认 32000，允许 1024–96000） - ``tool_result_thread_budget_chars``：单条 "
"TOOL_RESULT_JSON 序列化预算（默认 65536） - ``profile_max_chars`` / "
"``profile_truncate_chars``：profile 写入 Identity 前的截断上限（默认 4000） - "
"``bash_retries`` / ``bash_timeout_retries``：bash 超时后的额外重试次数（写入 "
"``LoopConfig.bash_retries``，默认 1，即共 2 次执行） - "
"``llm_transient_retries``：thread 压缩等直连 ``acompletion`` 遇瞬时错误时的最大重试次数（默认 "
"2） - ``tool_decision_max_retries``：传给 "
"``acompletion_with_pydantic_validation`` 的 max_retries（默认 10） - ``model``"
" / ``llm_model``：LiteLLM 路由模型名（用于 token_counter 与 tiktoken 回退） - "
"``tiktoken_encoding``：强制指定 tiktoken 编码名（默认 ``cl100k_base``）"
msgstr ""
"Flattened parameters passed to ``AgentConfig.from_kwargs`` (excerpt): - "
"``max_tool_rounds``: maximum number of tool rounds in a single step, "
"default 24 - ``preload_workspace_paths``: list of files to preload as "
"workspace snapshots injected into the system prompt - "
"``thread_key_state_paths``: list of KEY_STATE_JSON file paths included "
"during thread compaction - ``system_prompt_max_identity_chars``: maximum "
"total length of Agent Identity JSON, default 10000 - "
"``workspace_read_chunk_chars``: maximum characters per chunk for "
"``workspace_read`` / ``read_skill``, default 32000, allowed range "
"1024-96000 - ``tool_result_thread_budget_chars``: serialization budget "
"for a single TOOL_RESULT_JSON item, default 65536 - ``profile_max_chars``"
" / ``profile_truncate_chars``: truncation limit before profile content is"
" written into Identity, default 4000 - ``bash_retries`` / "
"``bash_timeout_retries``: additional retries after bash timeout, written "
"into ``LoopConfig.bash_retries``, default 1, meaning up to 2 executions "
"in total - ``llm_transient_retries``: maximum retries for transient "
"errors in direct ``acompletion`` calls such as thread compaction, default"
" 2 - ``tool_decision_max_retries``: ``max_retries`` passed to "
"``acompletion_with_pydantic_validation``, default 10 - ``model`` / "
"``llm_model``: LiteLLM routed model name, used by ``token_counter`` and "
"tiktoken fallback - ``tiktoken_encoding``: explicit tiktoken encoding "
"name, default ``cl100k_base``"

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.__init__:7 of
msgid "传入 ``AgentConfig.from_kwargs()`` 的扁平参数（节选）："
msgstr "Flattened parameters passed to ``AgentConfig.from_kwargs`` (excerpt):"

