"1, that is, 2 executions in total)"

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.__init__:17 of
msgid "``llm_transient_retries``：thread 压缩等直连 ``acompletion`` 遇瞬时错误时的最大重试次数（默认 2）"
msgstr ""
"``llm_transient_retries``: direct connection such as thread compression "
"``acompletion`` Maximum number of retries in case of transient error "
"(default 2)"

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.__init__:18 of
msgid ""
"``tool_decision_max_retries``：传给 ``acompletion_with_pydantic_validation``"
