msgid "初始化运行时目录，加载持久配置并扫描 custom/env skills。"
msgstr ""
"Initialize the runtime directory, load persistent configuration and scan "
"custom/env skills."

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.init:3 of
msgid ""
"流程： 1. 调用父类 init 2. 确保 agent 工作目录存在 3. 从 init_state 初始化 workspace 4. "
"加载持久化的 agent_config.json 5. 扫描环境模块提供的 skills 6. 刷新可见技能列表 7. 激活环境模块声明的默认技能"
" 8. 获取世界描述"
msgstr ""
"Process: 1. Call the parent class init 2. Ensure that the agent working "
"directory exists 3. Initialize the workspace from init_state 4. Load the "
"persistent agent_config.json 5. Scan the skills provided by the "
"environment module 6. Refresh the visible skills list 7. Activate the "
"default skills declared by the environment module 8. Get the world "
"description"

