#: ../../api/agent.rst:36
msgid ""
"``AgentBase`` 只规定智能体必须具备的最小生命周期接口。``PersonAgent`` 在此基础上增加了 "
"workspace、技能目录、工具循环、检查点与上下文压缩等运行时能力。"
msgstr ""
"``AgentBase`` only specifies the minimum life cycle interface that the "
"agent must have. ``PersonAgent`` On this basis, runtime capabilities such"
" as workspace, skill catalog, tool loop, checkpoint and context "
"compression are added."

#: ../../api/agent.rst:38
msgid ""
"如果只是扩展人物行为，优先新增或修改 Agent Skill；只有需要改变智能体生命周期、状态机或外部系统调用方式时，才继承 "
"``AgentBase`` / ``PersonAgent`` 创建新类。技能系统的设计说明见 :doc:`/agent_skills`，API "
"参考见 :doc:`/api/skills`。"
msgstr ""
"If you only want to extend agent behavior, prefer adding or modifying an "
"Agent Skill; only inherit from ``AgentBase`` / ``PersonAgent`` to create a "
"new class when you need to change the agent lifecycle, state machine, or "
"external system interaction patterns. See :doc:`/agent_skills` for the "
"skill system design guide, and see :doc:`/api/skills` for the API "
"reference."

