"ExperimentInfo: Basic experiment information object, including: - "
"experiment_id: experiment ID - hypothesis_id: hypothesis ID - status: "
"experiment status (not_started/running/completed/failed) - start_time: "
"start time - end_time: end time - agent_count: number of Agents - "
"step_count: number of executed steps"

