#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.sync_simulation_clock:1 of
msgid "与编排器当前仿真时刻对齐。"
msgstr "Aligned with the current simulation moment of the orchestrator."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.sync_simulation_clock:3 of
msgid ""
"``ask``/codegen 的 InitStage 用 ``self.t`` 写入 ``ctx['current_time']``。 若仅在 "
"``env_router.step`` 末尾才更新 ``self.t``，而 agent 先执行，则整步内时钟落后一步。 任何复制 "
"``AgentSociety.step`` 顺序（先 agent 后 env.step）的代码都应在 agent 开始前调用本方法。"
msgstr ""
"The InitStage of ``ask``/codegen writes ``ctx['current_time']`` with "
"``self.t``. If ``self.t`` is updated only at the end of "
"``env_router.step``, and the agent is executed first, the clock will be "
"one step behind in the entire step. Any code that replicates the "
"``AgentSociety.step`` sequence (agent first, then env.step) should call "
"this method before the agent starts."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.ask:1 of
