msgstr ""
"Override to return a skill name, e.g. ``return \"public-goods-"
"experiment\"`` to auto-activate that skill."

#: agentsociety2.env.base.EnvBase.get_default_skill:18 of
msgid ""
"**Note:** The skill must be available (either built-in or discovered via "
