#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter:3 of
msgid ""
"工作流程： 1. 收集所有环境模块的工具信息 2. 使用LLM的function calling能力选择并调用工具 3. 执行工具调用，获取结果 "
"4. 将结果反馈给LLM，继续下一轮Reasoning-Acting循环 5. 直到LLM判断任务完成或达到最大步数"
msgstr ""
"Workflow: 1. Collect tool information of all environment modules 2. Use "
"LLM's function calling capability to select and call tools 3. Execute "
"tool calls and obtain results 4. Feed back the results to LLM and "
"continue the next Reasoning-Acting cycle 5. Until LLM determines that the"
" task is completed or the maximum number of steps is reached"

