"steps in the plan."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter:3 of
msgid ""
"工作流程： 1. 收集所有环境模块的工具信息 2. 第一阶段：使用LLM制定执行计划（不调用工具） 3. 第二阶段：按照计划逐步执行工具调用 4."
" 根据执行结果生成最终答案"
msgstr ""
"Workflow: 1. Collect tool information from all environment modules 2. "
"Phase 1: Use LLM to develop an execution plan (without calling tools) 3. "
"Phase 2: Execute tool calls step by step according to the plan 4. "
"Generate the final answer based on the execution results"

